Workflow:

1. Add video to src/

2. Create dataset
> python make_dataset.py src/VIDEO.mp4 datasets/DATASET

3. Use labelme to label images in datasets/DATASET/images/train and datasets/DATASET/images/val

4. Create YOLO compatible labels
> python make_labels.py datasets/DATASET

5. Create dataset manifest DATA.yaml with all desired datasets

6. Train model
> python train.py DATA.yaml models/MODEL.pt

7. Test model
> python test.py models/MODEL.pt src/VIDEO.mp4 results/OUTPUT.mp4
